data.description:
This is an amazing opportunity to own a great property in the wonderful area of BELL MEADOWS!
Situated on a beautiful shaded lot in a quiet cul-de-sac this property has the perfect mix of charm, features, and VALUE!
I dare you to find a better deal on a 4Bed, 2Bath home. Especially one featuring an eat in kitchen, hardwoods throughout, a formal dining room, formal living room, and Florida room with a bar! 

There was exceptional care taken while planning every inch of the 2700 square feet. As you enter the front door you are greeted by an elegant foyer with a massive formal dining room to your left. This property has gorgeous worm hardwood floors throughout all the common areas. 

The formal living area is truly something to behold with a fireplace that features a painted brick accent wall and trayed ceiling. 

The Kitchen features a double oven and gas range. The design of this space is flexible enough to accommodate meals for loved ones on a weeknight or preparing a feast for extended family during the holidays! The former garage has been converted into a Florida room with ceramic tile, a wet bar and tons of natural lighting. 

The oversized bed rooms are masterpieces in their own right, featuring a main suite with double vanities, a walk-in closet, and separate toilet/tub room. 

As you walk onto the back deck, envision yourself out in nature listening to the birds chirping under mature trees overlooking a beautifully landscaped back yard.

Located off of Bell Rd. you will be only minutes away from great shopping, both retail and grocery. This location also provides easy access to the interstate, providing great commute times no matter where you are working.
ALL ITEMS WILL BE REMOVED FROM HOME BEFORE CLOSING AND WILL BE PROFESSIONALLY CLEANED! SELLER IS WILLING TO PAY FOR A HOME WARRANTY!
